{"data_series_issue_identification_fra": "1.1", "catalog_type": "Geo Data | G\\u00e9o", "title_fra": "EPSG Geodetic Parameter Registry", "data_series_issue_identification": "1.1", "ready_to_publish": "0", "digital_object_identifier": "", "subject": "", "data_series_name_fra": "CanTopo", "spatial_representation_type": "Map Digital | Carte num\u00e9rique", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "As Needed | Au besoin", "author": "Natural Resources Canada | Ressources naturelles Canada", "author_email": "", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "CanTopo est la nouvelle g\u00e9n\u00e9ration de cartes topographiques produites par Ressources naturelles Canada. Ce produit cartographique num\u00e9rique provient des meilleures sources de donn\u00e9es disponibles couvrant le territoire canadien et offre un produit cartographique de qualit\u00e9 en formats vectoriel et matriciel qui est conforme aux normes g\u00e9omatiques internationales.  CanTopo est un produit de sources multiples g\u00e9n\u00e9r\u00e9 \u00e0 partie de la Base de donn\u00e9es cartographique (BDC) d\u00e9crite dans les Sp\u00e9cifications de produit de la Base de donn\u00e9es cartographiques. Les donn\u00e9es de la BDC proviennent principalement de l'initiative G\u00e9oBase (www.geobase.ca), des donn\u00e9es topographiques num\u00e9riques de Ressources naturelles Canada et de donn\u00e9es d'initiatives nationales. Des donn\u00e9es de sources faisant autorit\u00e9 telles que provenant d'autres agences gouvernementales autant f\u00e9d\u00e9rales que provinciales, sont utilis\u00e9es entrepos\u00e9es et identifi\u00e9es.", "presentation_form": "Map Digital | Carte num\u00e9rique", "spatial": "{\"type\": \"Polygon\", \"coordinates\": [[[-83.5, 62.75], [-83.5, 63], [-83, 63], [-83, 62.75], [-83.5, 62.75]]]}", "license_id": "", "resources": [], "browse_graphic_url": "", "topic_category": "Imagery Base Maps Earth Cover  Imagerie carte de base couverture terrestre", "tags": [{"name": "CANTOPO045J141.0  CANTOPO045J141.0"}, {"name": "Earth Science  Sciences de la Terre"}, {"name": "Science Keywords BIOSPHERE VEGETATION  Mots-cl\u00e9s scientifiques biosph\u00e8re v\u00e9g\u00e9tation"}, {"name": "Administratives Boundaries  Limites administratives"}, {"name": "Buildings and Structures  B\u00e2timents et structures"}, {"name": "Energy  \u00c9nergie"}, {"name": "Hydrography  Hydrographie"}, {"name": "Industrial and Commercial Areas  Zones industrielles et commerciales"}, {"name": "Places of Interest  Lieux dint\u00e9r\u00eats"}, {"name": "Relief and Landforms  Relief et formes"}, {"name": "ToponymyPlace Names  ToponymieNoms de lieux"}, {"name": "Water Saturated Soils  Sols satur\u00e9s deau"}, {"name": "045J14  045J14"}], "endpoint_url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "date_published": "2010-11-02", "time_period_coverage_start": "1978-07-30", "data_series_name": "CanTopo", "endpoint_url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "time_period_coverage_end": "1978-07-30", "name": "0190339e-7748-405e-8a21-3a0ecbed7355", "language": "", "url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/0190339e-7748-405e-8a21-3a0ecbed7355.html", "notes": "CanTopo is the next generation of topographic maps being produced by Natural Resources Canada. This digital cartographic product originates from the best available data sources covering the Canadian territory and offers a quality cartographic product in vector and raster format that complies with international geomatics standards.  CanTopo is a multi-source product generated from the Cartographic Data Base (CDB) described in the Cartographic Data Base (CDB) Product Specification. Data within the CDB comes mainly from the GeoBase initiative (www.geobase.ca), Natural Resources Canada digital topographic data and data from national initiatives. Data from authoritative sources, such as other government agencies both federal and provincial, are identified, stored, and used.", "title": "EPSG Geodetic Parameter R